review.reviewText: Consistent construction of BBs. Adequately round. Does not jam AEG airsoft.

865932.title: Bulldog 0.12g 5000 Yellow Airsoft BB Pellets
feature: UKs Best Selling BB Pellets Now in the U.S.
description: These 0.12g 6mm Bulldog Airsoft BB Pellets have been designed to optimise the performance of spring operated Airsoft guns and pistols. You will be surprised just how good your entry level Airsoft gun will operate with this pro grade BB pellets! This ammo is calibrated and has a smooth polished surface, with no ridges or imperfections making this product the best you can buy for your 6mm Airsoft Gun.
